Todoroki: Shinsou and Aizawa physically resemble one another and their quirks are of similar nature, they appear very close too. Secret adopted son

summary: Theory: Izuku has/had AFO and his obsession with analyzing quirks is an effect of his AFO quirk.
question: Theory: Izuku has/had AFO and his obsession with analyzing quirks is an effect of his AFO quirk.
answer:
man I love this idea and it fits so well.

We know that quirks influence personalities (Bakugou is explosive, Uraraka lighthearted etc) but Izuku is quirkless, right? But one of his defining traits is his love of quirks and his ability to understand them. You know who else likes quirks and knows how they work?? All For One. I absolutely think this is a side effect of AFO teh quirk. His brain is hardwired to be able to sift through and understand quirks, his brain needs to be able to handle multiple different quirks of varying shapes and sizes. 

I do theorize Izuku got a functionally useless version of AFO, one where he can only receive multiple quirks and not give/take but thats a whole another discussion

summary: Howdy! So, Halloween is my favorite holiday ever and I've always enjoyed it, but this Halloween has just been horrible for me...
question: Howdy! So, Halloween is my favorite holiday ever and I've always enjoyed it, but this Halloween has just been horrible for me and I've been upset for an entire 24 hours now. Would you mind writing for Shouto and Bakugou with an s/o who is in the same situation as me??? (Shameless self insert lmao) thanks !!♥♥
answer:
I’m sorry you’ve had a bad Halloween! I hope these help.

~~~~~~~~~

Bakugou:

-Halloween isn’t really his favorite holiday, but if you aren’t having a good day he’ll try to make it somewhat better.

-He’ll still be his grumpy self though, just a tad bit sweeter. He’ll deal with anything you want to do even if he doesn’t want to do it.

-Costume shopping? He’ll hate it, but he’ll come. Candy shopping? He’ll most likely look for his favorite but he’ll still come.

Todoroki:

-He isn’t really a big fan of Halloween, but it hurts his heart to see you sad since you make him happy.

-He’ll try on a costume for you, even if it is ridiculous at least he’s trying. (He wore a clown costume.)

-His favorite candy is anything chocolate, so you bet your ass he’ll come candy shopping with you.
